description: Disassociates a Firewall Manager policy administrator from a third-party firewall tenant. When you call DisassociateThirdPartyFirewall, the third-party firewall vendor deletes all of the firewalls that are associated with the account.

parameters.name: ThirdPartyFirewall
parameters.description: The name of the third-party firewall vendor.

nested_items.name: ThirdPartyFirewallStatus
nested_items.description: The current status for the disassociation of a Firewall Manager administrators account with a third-party firewall.
